        <heading>Construction contracts; designations</heading>
        <content>
          <p>  ยง 1168.  Construction contracts; designations.  The contracts for the\nconstruction of eligible projects constructed and financed pursuant to a\nfinancing agreement shall be subject to the requirements and provisions\nof article fifteen-A of the executive law and, for such purposes, any\nsuch contract shall be considered a "state contract" and the department\nshall be the "contracting agency" for each such contract.\n</p>
